	Colours will change the colours and let you save them to a executable
	file

	Colours will ONLY run on AmigaDos 2.04

Note:

	Use Colours at your own risk.

Starting:

	»» Workbench ««

        Click on Colours twice.

    »» Cli ««

        Colours

Usage:

		Menus -

            About		- About Requester.

            Save		- Save colurs as Executable file, when clicked on
						  will change the colours.

            Quit		- Quit and restore starting colours.

            Reset to
			Default		- Reset colours to deafult.

            Restore		- Restore colours to starting colours.

			Preset		- Predefined colours.

            Save Icon	- If on will save icon when you save the Executable
                          file.

		Gadgets -

            Save		- Save colurs as Executable file, when clicked on
						  will change the colours.

            Use			- Quit and use colours.

			Cancel		- Quit and restore colours to starting colours.

		Keys -

			Amiga S		- Save colurs as Executable file, when clicked on
						  will change the colours.

            Amiga Q		- Quit and use colours.

            Amiga 1 to
			Amiga 9		- Predefined colours.

